  "verificationNotes": "CORRECTED paramsB from 2.63 to 2.53: HF model card architecture table states '2.5B' active/total params (dense, no MoE); independently re-derived from config.json (hidden_size=2048, 40 layers, intermediate=8192, vocab=49155, tie_word_embeddings=true, GQA 32 heads/8 KV) giving ~2.53B, matching IBM's own figure and Granite 3.3 2B's published 2.53B for the same architecture family. All 8 benchmark rows (MMLU 56.03, HellaSwag 76.79, IFEval 46.07, MMLU-Pro 27.92, SIQA 66.36, OBQA 43.2, AGI-Eval 29.75, MT-Bench 7.66) confirmed literally present on the cited HF model card. Release date/license/12-language claim confirmed via HF card and IBM newsroom announcement."
